{"id":46903,"type":3,"name":"夏の幻","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/4b/56/46903_jp.jpg","rating":{"total":17,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":1,"7":3,"8":7,"9":5,"10":0},"score":7.8},"summary":"柯南 ED10 第205話 - 第218話（計14話）\r\n《夏之幻》（日语：夏の幻）为GARNET CROW的第五张单曲。\r\n2000年10月25日发售。作词为AZUKI七，作曲为中村由利，编曲为古井弘人。\r\n\r\n3个月连续发售的第二枚单曲。此曲是由从发售时期和标题《夕阳》中想像二创作出来的歌曲。根据为动画演唱的歌曲记录了长期的销售品。在单曲的销量上为第四位。（作为《名侦探柯南》的片尾曲，歌曲和使用的视频也以夕阳为主题。）\r\n\r\n《名侦探柯南》所使用的版本和CD版的编曲稍有不同。\r\n\r\n这首歌曲也有别的编曲版本《夏の幻 (secret arrange ver.)》（收录于第一张专辑《first soundscope 〜水のない晴れた海へ〜》・第一张精选辑《Best》・第二张精选辑《THE BEST History of GARNET CROW at the crest...》。\r\n\r\n在2006年的全日本国民美少女比赛中，Grand Prix获奖者林丹丹作为正式选拔的选手和演技，一起热情的唱了这首歌。\r\n","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>夏之幻</li><li><span>艺术家: </span><a href=\"/person/9957\">GARNET CROW</a></li><li><span>厂牌: </span><a href=\"/person/13308\">GIZA studio</a></li><li><span>录音: </span><a href=\"/person/13308\">GIZA studio</a></li><li><span>版本特性: </span>Maxi</li><li><span>发售日期: </span>2000-10-25</li><li><span>价格: </span>￥ 1,050</li><li><span>播放时长: </span>12 m</li><li><span>发行商: </span>GIZA studio</li>","collection":{"collect":23},"tags":[{"name":"2000","count":3},{"name":"名探偵コナン","count":3},{"name":"ED","count":2},{"name":"GARNET_CROW","count":2},{"name":"anime","count":2},{"name":"名侦探柯南","count":2},{"name":"＊＊＊","count":1},{"name":"淡淡的忧伤","count":1},{"name":"single","count":1},{"name":"GARNET.CROW","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":0,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/0","type":0,"sort":0,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":""}],"disc":[{"title":"Disc 1","disc":[{"title":"1 夏の幻","href":"/ep/191377"},{"title":"2 hi-speed スペシャル oneday","href":"/ep/191378"},{"title":"3 夏の幻 (instrumental)","href":"/ep/191379"}]}],"staff":[{"id":9957,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/f6/1a/9957_prsn_73So6.jpg","name":"GARNET CROW","desc":"艺术家"},{"id":13308,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/16/7e/13308_prsn_31AQA.jpg","name":"GIZA studio","desc":"厂牌"}],"relations":[{"id":899,"image"